-- Air India, Boeing to Hold Talks Over Plane Delivery, Press Trust Reports
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-06-13T05:29:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/air-india-boeing-to-hold-talks-over-plane-delivery-press-trust-reports.html

          
          
             Air India and Boeing Co. will
discuss delays and compensation in delivering 27 Dreamliner
planes to the national carrier, the Press Trust of India
reported, without saying where it obtained the information. A
team of officials from Boeing will discuss with Air India
management issues such as aircraft deliveries, financing and
payment of compensation, the news agency said.  
